 A man named Taofeek Gbolagade has reportedly beaten his pregnant wife to stupor for failing to prepare Ramadan meal for him. Report had it that fight broke out between the couple living at the Ogbere Housing Estate in Ibadan, Oyo State around 4am, on Tuesday. A source alleged that “This man always beats his wife over little misunderstandings. I was able to record today’s event. He is a Muslim, so I think they had an argument over Sahur. “This man didn’t mind that she was pregnant with his second child and so, pounced on her. She wailed for hours before she was able to flee to her parents’ house. “Gbolagade has fled his house after being declared wanted by the security personnel.” Confirming the incident, the Police Public Relations Officer in the state, Adewale Osifeso, said that investigation had commenced on the matter and updates would be given in due course. 